Excited to see all the great conversations happening on Twitter. Our team is focused on promoting healthy discourse for all.
So many cool things happening in AI right now! Excited to see what people build.
With large models like GPT-4 on the horizon, it's an incredible time to be building in AI. The pace of progress is astonishing. Can't wait to see what emerges from the community!

Making great progress on my latest AI research project - hope to share an update soon!
Hey Harrison, this weekend I'm working on some new demos showing how LLMs can be integrated into business workflows. What are you building?
A few examples: chatbots for lead gen, AI writing for marketing copy, visual design generators. The key is focusing the AI on high value workflows.
